description: Tired of today's fast food culture? Well, so are we, and we're doing something about it in a big way. We are a mobile Peruvian food truck base in Los Angeles Area , serving hearty sandwiches stuffed with classic and contemporary Peruvian ingredients, traditional sides. INKANTO combines the experience of two worlds: one of eating satisfying “Street Food” and the other of enjoying high-quality ingredients and professional service that you find at a fine restaurant. We bring them both to your front door. From our heart to yours.. Enjoy!!
name: Inkanto Peruvian Gourmet
